OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with plenty of sunshine,
OL,6,Falthough it will often be hazy.
OL,7,FBecoming very warm or hot for most
OL,8,Fplaces away from the coast, where
OL,9,Fcooling onshore breezes will occur.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with a mix of cloudier
OL,12,Fconditions across western areas and
OL,13,Fclear periods further east. Light
OL,14,Fwinds inland but becoming breezy along
OL,15,Fthe south coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
