OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,6,Fpredominantly dry, with perhaps an odd
OL,7,Flight shower across western areas.
OL,8,FWarm for many places inland with light
OL,9,Fwinds, but breezy along the south
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fdry morning then rain spreads east,
OL,14,Fbecoming heavy overnight. Tuesday
OL,15,Fsunshine and showers, some heavy with
OL,16,Fperhaps hail and thunder. Wednesday
OL,17,Fmainly dry and fine before rain
OL,18,Farrives later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
